snippet.title: Underworld: The Eternal War - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Developed by Lucky Chicken Games (who also developed Aquaman: Battle for Atlantis) and published exclusively in Europe by System 3 under the Play It label, this is a 3D shooter based on the movie.

Underworld: The Eternal War (C) Subterranian Productions LLC.
